Description: At the base of the bridge's foundation you find a crevice small enough to crawl through - this must be the cave the smugglers were referring to. You crawl through the small opening and find yourself in a passageway large enough for you to stand. Another small fissure lies in front of you: as you approach it, the earth begins to shake and rumble.
DescriptionAction: It looks like the ceiling is caving in - better act fast!
